column1: IART reached a 52 Week low at 34.36

IART recently received a $70 price target, but the stock has fallen to close to $52. Earnings report seemed positive looking forward, so the stock seems like a buy at this level. Always a chance a bigger player may try to scoop them up. Good luck!
#IART has been showing support at 59.36 and resistance at 65.08. Buy rating: 6, target: 81.03, according to 9trading.
